data.description: Welcome to this charming single-family house located in the desirable Pelham area of the Bronx! This beautiful property offers a unique opportunity for both comfortable living and potential investment in a vibrant and sought-after neighborhood. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The house features a well-designed layout, with a total of five spacious bedrooms and two modern bathrooms, providing ample space or accommodating multiple occupants. Whether you're looking for a place to call home or seeking a rental property, this house has the versatility to suit your needs. The main living areas boast an abundance of natural light, creating a cheerful ambiance throughout. The open-concept design seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it an ideal space for hosting gatherings and spending quality time with loved ones. The kitchen is equipped with modern appliances, ample counter space, and stylish cabinetry, catering to the culinary enthusiast in you. Outside, the property offers a serene backyard, providing an oasis of relaxation and recreation for outdoor activities, barbecues, or gardening. One of the biggest advantages of this property is its prime location in Pelham, a highly sought-after residential area in the Bronx. Residents enjoy convenient access to an array of amenities, including local shops, restaurants, parks, and excellent schools. The neighborhood's close-knit community and friendly atmosphere make it a wonderful place to call home. With its spacious layout, modern amenities, and prime location, this home is a true gem that offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for all its occupants. Don't miss out on the chance to make this wonderful property your own!
